    "asOf": "2020-05-08",
    "date": "2020-10-29T15:20:47Z",
    "text": "Business Borrowers Protection Act \n\nThis bill prohibits a creditor from enforcing a loan covenant that requires the accelerated repayment of a loan if the borrower receives a loan under certain COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) economic aid programs. Additionally, a creditor is prohibited from enforcing any loan covenant beginning on the date of enactment of this bill and ending one year after the termination of the COVID-19 national emergency."
  },
